{"tid":251730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國公布戰績: 已經殺了7.6萬名伊斯蘭國武裝份子","createTime":"2017-05-21T07:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T09:59:45.000Z","uid":53705,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1253fad16c1ef50c054a7b864da24177f70df86c","tid":251730,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:36:18.000Z","msg":"-美軍空襲從開始到2016年8月為止共打死超過4.5萬IS<br />\n-在拉馬迪戰役殺死400名IS<br />\n-費盧傑殺死3500名伊斯蘭國<br />\n-曼比季戰役打死IS計4200人<br />\n-巴蔔戰役，土軍殺IS達2647人<br />\n<br />\n-摩蘇爾戰役最新數據是已殺IS 1.6萬<br />\n摩蘇爾最新的美伊聯合指揮部戰果統計。2016年攻城以來，聯軍共計擊斃16467伊國武裝分子，679輛伊斯蘭國汽車炸彈被摧毀&bull;6661個炸彈被排除&bull;217自殺背心被清除&bull;47架無人機被摧毀。<br />\n<br />\n至此，死於美國及盟友打擊下的IS共計至少7.6萬人<br />\n而伊拉克軍隊和民兵陣亡1.6萬人<br />\n庫爾德自治區部隊陣亡1600人<br />\n美軍亡36人，其中非戰鬥死亡27人。英國、加拿大和德國各犧牲1人。"},{"pid":"dce77a56541608bede5a4317ef6dc39494e640cc","tid":251730,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"公佈埋呢啲數據只會令整個回教世界更憎恨美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地心諗:公平咩,夠膽落黎同我隻揪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f0aa8dfe6e3202cbe23cbfa2e0d174651a0ec7","tid":251730,"uid":41508,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8393d678f4ab9149c4d4b731c90df00084af37d0","tid":251730,"uid":28558,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:39:33.000Z","msg":"究竟邊個先係恐佈份子呢...."},{"pid":"66608884788ee3efba40b299c97f9bbf78d1d422","tid":251730,"uid":40216,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟邊個先係恐佈份子呢....</blockquote><br />\n唔滿意你咪去加入伊斯蘭國咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abb3a47d4ffc6a0edceb675eced0203fdb71743","tid":251730,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T07:41:33.000Z","